Summary: While driving from an ecotourist reservation the asa-wright nature reserve I took a photo of a tree,later after uploading the photo's I saw this object in the picture
divs: sighting detailsmy partner and myself were visiting the asa-wright nature center on sunday the 21st of febuary.we were there for aproximately 3 hours.during the entire day we had been taking photograghs of the country side and towns.upon leaving we continued taking photo's,i pointed out an orange colored floweing poui tree and took a photo,it took us about 1 1\2 hours to get back to where were were staying.as usual i uploaded the photograghs to my computer and while looking through them i noticed what appeared to be a spot on one of the photo's.i checked all the photo's of the day and there was not anything simular on the other photo's,checked and double checked all the photo's and am left with an unexplained object on the one photo.i am interested to if possible have the photo reviewed. thank you rr
